race.comment: VICTORY QUEEN (3) was strong to the line when chasing into a close third at Clare. Sure to have tightened from that run and will appreciate the extra 100m. Can get the job done. LIKE A DIAMOND (2) was good here fresh when chasing into third, then left with too much to do last time but finished off strongly. Peaking now and can give this a big shake. LADY OF SAVOY (5) caught the eye last start when rattling home to just miss. Can build off that effort and Pannell's booking is a strong push. EXALTED KATE (4) doesn't win often but has improved in her last two and looks ready to play a major role. BRISEIS ECLIPSE (1) is mixing her form but gets the chance to put it all together this time.
